properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Ah, hello there. The fishing's been good, thanks for asking. The sea has been generous to me today. 

Aye, there are a few things you should keep in mind if you want to survive on Rivenn. First and foremost, dress warmly. The temperature here is always below freezing, so you'll want to make sure you're well insulated. And be on the lookout for the yeti, a legendary beast said to roam these lands. If you see one, run the other way, or you'll end up as its next meal. Other than that, just use your common sense, and you should be alright.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Rivenn, a land of stark beauty and resilient people, is haunted by a dark legend—the yeti. This monstrous creature, said to roam the icy wilderness, has brought sorrow directly to my doorstep, slaughtering my family in a ruthless display of savagery. Driven by an unquenchable fury, I vow to traverse the perilous wilds, confront this abomination, and avenge the spirits of my kin. The yeti, a symbol of terror and pain, must be vanquished for peace to return to our snow-laden realm.

Amidst this grim vendetta, Rivenn's spirit endures through its vibrant traditions and skilled craftspeople. The community thrives, celebrating life with festivals and cherishing the warmth of togetherness. As I steel myself against the cold both without and within, I carry the flame of hope and determination. The yeti's reign of terror will end, and from the ashes of grief, our people's resilience will forge a stronger, undaunted Rivenn.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value:
Lumberjacking is a tough, but rewarding job. The forests of Rivenn are filled with tall, ancient trees, and it's our job to carefully harvest them for their wood. It's important work, as wood is a vital resource for our community. We use it for everything from building homes and furniture, to keeping warm during the long, cold winters.

But it's not all easy work. The forests of Rivenn are filled with dangers, from wild animals like winter wolves and harsh weather. We have to be constantly vigilant and prepared for anything. But the satisfaction of a job well done, and the knowledge that we are helping to provide for our community, makes it all worth it.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! I will tell you a very special legend! The villagers of Rivenn Island angered the powerful god Zoltar by becoming complacent and not making offerings to him. In his wrath, he placed a curse on the village causing famine and disease. The villagers sought the help of the village shaman who advised them to make a grand offering of gems and gold to Zoltar to show their repentance. The offering pleased Zoltar and he lifted the curse and blessed the village with prosperity once again. From then on, the villagers made sure to honor and respect Zoltar to avoid another curse.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! An expedition has been sent to study the Winter Wolves living on the remote island of Rivenn. They discovered that these wolves possessed a developed intelligence and a mysterious leader, the Alpha Wolf, who would do anything to protect his pack and territory from intruders. Help this team and kill 7 Winter Wolves!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! A small village on Rivenn Island is faced with a strange and frightening situation, mysterious storms, frozen lakes and the disappearance of a few residents. As you explore, you'll discover that the village is under the curse of a wild polar bear. Kill 4 polar bears to lift the curse and restore peace to society!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! There are rumors of strange noises and movements coming from a frozen cave on Rivenn Island. As a brave adventurer, it's up to you to investigate and discover the source of the disturbance. If you see Goblins there, feel free to kill them!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! A group of frost salamanders, creatures native to Rivenn Island, are exhibiting strange behavior and causing disturbances in the nearby village. Find and kill 5 frost salamanders. But be careful, because the curse is powerful and frost salamanders aren't the only danger you'll face in this quest.

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! A small village on Rivenn Island is under the curse of an ancient and powerful god. Listen to the magic story from the village shaman to lift the curse of this powerful being!

properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Hey {{char.name}}! Search the island of Rivenn Island to track down a missing group of explorers and bring them back safely, there is a plan to exploit the island's resources, find the climber and listen to her advice to stop it!
